{
  "stem": "10353.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we sort of let loose there and we raided that place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we tried to stuff ourselves with whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we were crawling from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I was just crawling under-- under one of the freight cars to go into another freight car when one of the Sonderwaffen-- what they called it-- these were in the black uniforms with a-- shoved a pistol against me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He says-- and he didn't shoot, but he yelled in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN]-- this is enough, get back, which we did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We were traveling for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] several days, because the train apparently was zig-zagging, trying to get through the Elbe River.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She couldn't get through the Elbe River, because they were cut off, 'til finally they found one place where we-- they-- they got through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And after several days of travel, we finally came into Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "In Theresienstadt, we were thrown into a pit that apparently was an old castle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And this was the back part of a castle with a tunnel underneath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And it was a very, very rainy day, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And we were kept there for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "During the night, we sort of managed to smuggle into that tunnel, to try to be shielded from-- from the rain.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we were-- about two days later, we were marched out from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we were taken into one of the armories, because Theresienstadt was composed of many armories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were taken into the-- what was it called now, the name of the city?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Dresdner Kaserne, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were billeted in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now this was already solid buildings-- it wasn't barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Solid buildings.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- for our group, I was given the task to haul coal from the basement up to the second floor where the kitchen was situated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there it was regularly given already soup every-- every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to haul that coal back and forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, at night, we were given the task to clean up the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a little bit of privilege.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got a little bit of extra soup for that work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we knew that typhoid was on the breakout.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We heard already isolated cases.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every day you heard more and more that typhoid is breaking out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was going on 'til [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] May, May 9th.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On May 9th, in the evening, we were doing our usual work cleaning up the kitchen around 9:00, 9:30 in the evening, when my fellow worker, whom I refer to as a German Jew, young, younger man, we were cleaning up the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was looking down from the second floor window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he saw some people in strange uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he told me in German, he says, oh, he says, they must be some French prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't pay too much attention, until about 50 minutes later, a Russian tank moved through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then the Russian army started to move in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we knew already there was a whole, whole upheaval in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody's dancing and jumping, you know, the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "With us knowing that-- the way typhoid was breaking out-- we were determined the following morning to leave camp and to go towards Prague, which we did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We walked for about six to eight kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to turn back, because the Germans were still fighting on and there was still heavy activity going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we went back to the-- to the camp-- to the Dresdner Kaserne.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we waited 'til the following morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The following morning around 4:00 o'clock in the morning, we got up and we started to walk towards Prague.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we walked and we walked and we walked all day long, 'til around noontime we caught onto a Russian column, a horse-- a horse-drawn wagon.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we begged them that they should take us on, which they did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they took us on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we traveled with them, until we came to a village in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were, but we traveled with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they-- they drove into a farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there they organized themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they cooked themselves a goulash there, with cabbage soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was the first time that they gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Early in the morning, the following morning, they got up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we went with them for a little while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then they said they are turning off this road, and if we want to go to Prague, we have to go straight.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came into Saturday.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
